en_910494_0	Ven Diyasenpura Wimala Thero, the renowned meditation practitioner at ‘Bavunseth Mind Relaxing Meditation Centre’ at Hellummahara, Dekatana held another meditation session for one Officer and forty-eight Other Ranks of the Sri Lanka Army on Monday (7).
en_910494_1	It was organized at the request of the Directorate of Psychological Operations at the Army Headquarters.
